### Arrest ages are fairly similar across sex groups, with males showing slightly more older outliers.

```{r}
age_sex_data <- arrests |>
  filter(!is.na(age), !is.na(sex)) |>
  filter(sex %in% c("F", "M")) |>
  mutate(
    sex = recode(sex,
                 "F" = "Female",
                 "M" = "Male")
  )

ggplot(age_sex_data,
       aes(x = sex,
           y = age,
